1. *Korist* mi je bila velika. (The benefit was great for me.)
2. Svi se nadamo da će taj događaj doneti korist za našu zajednicu. (We all hope that this event will bring benefit for our community.)
3. Ona je videla neke koristi od novog posla. (She saw some benefits from the new job.)
4. *Koristili* smo sve alate koje smo imali. (We used all the tools we had.)
5. Njihova *korisnost* je bila očigledna. (Their usefulness was obvious.)